name: CesareanSectionICD10PCS
title: Cesarean Section ICD10PCS
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values identifies patients who have a procedure of a Cesarean section.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients who have a Cesarean section procedure.  Using the Quality Data Model, this particular element will map to the Procedure category.),(Inclusion Criteria: Only use codes which represent Cesarean section procedures. Codes used are to be ICD10PCS codes only.),(Exclusion Criteria: None.)
